# GamesX Market 🎮

A full-stack marketplace app for trading in-game items securely.

## 🌍 Features

- 💰 Coin-based deposit/withdraw system
- 🛒 Item listing and browsing (React frontend)
- 🔐 JWT-based login & protected routes
- 🧾 Admin dashboard for transaction approvals
- 📦 PayPal integration (withdrawal payouts)
- 🔍 Search, filters, pagination
- ⭐ Seller rating system
- 📊 Trade history export (CSV)

## 🧠 Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** React + Tailwind CSS
- **Backend:** Node.js + Express
- **Database:** MongoDB + Mongoose
- **Auth:** JWT
- **Payments:** PayPal API
- **Cloud:** Firebase (if used)

## 🧪 How to Run Locally

### 🔧 Backend
```bash
cd game-hub-backend
npm install
npm start

💻 Frontend
cd game-hub-frontend
npm install
npm run dev

